name: Ned Kaye in: Void of the Mind
name_original: Ned Kaye in: Void of the Mind
description:
A thing I made for my e-fed. If you don't know what the XWF is, this probably isn't going to mean much to you, but if you're interested in wrestling roleplay online, check out xwf99.com!

Heavily inspired by Yume Nikki and its fangames. If you haven't played those, I would highly recommend them.
